data.text:
All-Star Variety Show

Nine all-star queens -- plus one unexpected competitor -- return to compete for the new crown and participate in a variety show, and debate breaks out over elimination strategies.

Forever Plaid

London's father is making her attend public school until she can get her grades up, but Maddie is worried that if London goes to her school that she's going take away what popularity she has and steal all the attention as usual.

Neither a Borrower Nor a Speller Bee

Cody is ecstatic because he's now the favorite to win the Boston Spelling Bee. But after Zack borrows money from Cody's toughest competitor and has not way of paying him back, Zack is forced to ask Cody to throw the competition so competitor will forgive his brother's debts.
